# Redesign Plan: HCAA-INDUSTRIAL (Target: rbxprogramming.com)

## Goal
Redesign the HCAA landing page to match the visual style, layout, and "industrial tech" aesthetic of [rbxprogramming.com](https://rbxprogramming.com/).

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a **complete visual overhaul**.
> - **Theme Change**: Moving from Dark/Cyan to **Industrial Dark/White/Orange (#FE3800)**.
> - **Font Change**: Switching to **DM Sans** for all text.
> - **Layout Change**: Reordering sections to match the target site (Hero -> Services Grid -> Features -> Stats Bar -> Why Us List -> Contact).

## Proposed Changes

### Assets & Design System
#### [MODIFY] [style.css](file:///c:/HCAA-INDUSTRIAL/style.css)
- Import **DM Sans** from Google Fonts.
- Update CSS Variables:
    - Primary Color: `#FE3800` (Orange)
    - backgrounds: Mix of `#FFFFFF` (Content), `#000000` (Footer), Dark Overlay (Hero).
- Implement new utility classes for:
    - "Ghost" buttons (Orange border, transparent fill).
    - Big Outlined Numbers (for "Why Us" section).
    - Stats Bar styling.

### Structure & Content
#### [MODIFY] [index.html](file:///c:/HCAA-INDUSTRIAL/index.html)
- **Header**: Simplify. Logo Left, Hamburger Right (visual only for now), Clean Nav.
- **Hero**: Align left. Big bold typography. "Ghost" button.
- **Services**: Convert to 2x2 Grid or clean cards.
- **[NEW SECTION] Stats Bar**: "In Figures" section (Orange background).
- **Why Us**: Redesign as a list with large outlined numbers (01, 02...).
- **Footer**: Redesign with high contrast Black/Orange.

#### [MODIFY] [main.js](file:///c:/HCAA-INDUSTRIAL/main.js)
- Ensure existing logic (Forms, Dates) still works with new ID/classes.
- Update animations if needed to match the "industrial" feel.

## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- None (Visual refactor).

### Manual Verification
1. **Visual Check**: Open [index.html](file:///c:/HCAA-INDUSTRIAL/index.html) in browser. Compare side-by-side with rbxprogramming.com screenshots/memory.
2. **Responsiveness**: Check mobile view (hamburger menu appearance, stacking order).
3. **Interactivity**: Test the Contact Form submission (ensure it still hits the webhook).
4. **Hover Effects**: Verify buttons and cards have the correct hover states.
